naye portselan,

00:15:18.753 --> 00:15:22.596
dos hot men gehaltn SPECIAL oyf peysekh!

00:15:22.736 --> 00:15:24.429
un dos iz geven komplet!

00:15:24.429 --> 00:15:26.241
nay un sheyn!

00:15:26.988 --> 00:15:30.865
az ikh bin geven bagaystert.

00:15:31.055 --> 00:15:32.943
se hot farlangt a sakh arbet,

00:15:32.943 --> 00:15:34.915
ober dos iz geven di yontef.

00:15:36.118 --> 00:15:43.066
un un vos hot ayer mishpokhe getun oyf vakatsye? ir zent a mol avekgeforn oyf a vakatsye?

00:15:43.965 --> 00:15:50.018
mayn mameshi hot gehat a pasport

00:15:50.900 --> 00:15:52.549
a oyslendishn,

00:15:52.858 --> 00:15:58.270
un zi iz yedern yor geforn nokh Daytshland,

00:15:59.169 --> 00:16:01.088
un kur-ort,

00:16:02.865 --> 00:16:05.847
far dem me hot gehat a hoyz in BRESLAU,

00:16:05.936 --> 00:16:09.053
BRESLAU iz WROCŁAW yetst,

00:16:10.425 --> 00:16:14.082
in KUDOWA-ZDRÓJ iz geven a HERZBAD,

00:16:14.390 --> 00:16:18.547
di tateshi hot geshikt yederes yor

00:16:18.547 --> 00:16:20.800
di mameshi oyf zeks vokhn,

00:16:20.800 --> 00:16:23.211
geforn dortn,

00:16:25.072 --> 00:16:30.113
mameshi hot nisht getun keyn fizishe arbet, nor dos vos zi hot gelibt in der heym,

00:16:30.438 --> 00:16:34.367
in dortn iz zi geforn, hot zi mitgebrengt di kinder sheyne zakhn,

00:16:34.367 --> 00:16:38.595
un undz ze'mir geblibn n- nisht nor mitn meshores,

00:16:38.595 --> 00:16:42.364
nor me, zey hobn undz tsugenumen a kuzine,

00:16:44.613 --> 00:16:46.734
vos zenen nisht gevezn raykh,

00:16:46.908 --> 00:16:51.038
un zi hot oyfgepast oyfn hoyz un oyf di kinder.

00:16:51.532 --> 00:16:55.993
zeks vokhn. mameshi hot mir gebrengt a sheyne PRESENT.

00:16:55.993 --> 00:16:59.005
un dos hot gevezn...

00:16:59.005 --> 00:17:00.758
azoy, yedes yor.

00:17:00.729 --> 00:17:03.171
un ir zent oykhet a mol geforn ergets?

00:17:03.530 --> 00:17:06.562
ikh hob nisht gekont, me hot gemuzt hobn a pasport

00:17:06.855 --> 00:17:08.200
nokh oysland.

00:17:08.272 --> 00:17:09.509
mayn mameshi

00:17:09.509 --> 00:17:14.038
hot es gehat pro- di day- protektsye, mit protektsye hot zi gekrign,

00:17:14.415 --> 00:17:18.268
yedes yor hot men ir banayt a pasport,

00:17:18.268 --> 00:17:23.252
in Poyln iz nisht gevezn. ikh hob geku-, ikh hob gezegnt mayn mameshi,

00:17:23.443 --> 00:17:28.477
nor m- in di shto-, a shtetl, nisht vayt fun WIELUŃ,

00:17:28.477 --> 00:17:30.475
se hot geheysn PRASZKA,

00:17:30.547 --> 00:17:32.770
un dortn iz geven di grenets,

00:17:32.927 --> 00:17:36.701
un s'iz geven, di grenets iz geven oyf a brik,

00:17:37.382 --> 00:17:42.608
hob ikh nisht getort batretn di tsveyte zayt fun di brik

00:17:42.849 --> 00:17:46.204
far dem, dos iz shoyn geven Daytshland un dos iz geven Poyln!

00:17:46.204 --> 00:17:49.999
far mir iz es geven zeyer komish, ober dos iz gevezn di WAHRHEIT.

00:17:50.392 --> 00:17:53.638
un vi azoy hot ayer muter gehat aza protektsye?

00:17:53.638 --> 00:17:54.505
tsu forn?

00:17:55.218 --> 00:17:57.508
der tateshi iz gevezn klug,

00:17:59.927 --> 00:18:01.593
un di polyakn,

00:18:02.424 --> 00:18:05.608
di ongezeene, raykhe polyakn,

00:18:06.542 --> 00:18:09.490
hobn gefregt-n-im

00:18:09.579 --> 00:18:12.476
vos tsu tun, un er hot gehandlt mit zey,

00:18:12.903 --> 00:18:16.273
un er hot zey farbetn in di shtub arayn

00:18:16.667 --> 00:18:20.476
un oykh geganen dortn in hotel vu zey esn,

00:18:20.632 --> 00:18:22.804
un shtendik gevezn tsuzamet,

00:18:22.826 --> 00:18:27.076
zey hobn, zey hobn gevolt er zol trinken mit zey tsuzamet oykhet,

00:18:27.076 --> 00:18:32.221
nor der tateshi hot nisht gekent trinken, hot er, az zey hobn nisht gezen

00:18:32.293 --> 00:18:33.159
hot er g-,

00:18:33.159 --> 00:18:38.650
zey hobn ⟨ar⟩ayngegosn, hot dos glezl oysgegosn, zey hobn nisht gezen,

00:18:39.566 --> 00:18:44.353
un azoy hot er gehat protektsye bayn BURGERMEISTER,

00:18:44.645 --> 00:18:48.843
BURGERMEISTER iz der, prezident fun der shtot,

00:18:49.337 --> 00:18:52.487
un bay di hoypt doktoyrim oykhet.

00:18:53.471 --> 00:18:54.192
genoy.

00:18:54.213 --> 00:18:57.668
vos me hot gebroykht hot men gehat.

00:18:58.095 --> 00:19:00.655
er hot oykh gegebn matones.

00:19:01.368 --> 00:19:04.958
ikh gedenk az far CHRISTMAS

00:19:05.081 --> 00:19:08.198
iz di gantse shtub gevezn mit matones.

00:19:08.287 --> 00:19:13.473
un zeyer tayere mishp- matones! ikh hob mikh gevundert, me get azoy oys gelt!

00:19:13.473 --> 00:19:18.137
azelkhene sheyne fun Krak- hitelekh oyf vinter.

00:19:18.243 --> 00:19:24.518
un kragns, un hentshkes, ober alts di beste kvalitet hot er gegebn.

00:19:24.518 --> 00:19:28.077
un ⟨TRUNKI⟩ iz likern.

00:19:28.588 --> 00:19:30.102
vos zey hobn lib gehat.

00:19:30.984 --> 00:19:34.185
ir zent geven zeyer gut op, ir foter iz geven raykh?

00:19:34.629 --> 00:19:37.730
yo. undz hot mir gehat

00:19:38.139 --> 00:19:43.821
in vi ikh hob gezogt, in BRESLAU, in WIELUŃ, hayzer.

00:19:44.450 --> 00:19:54.994
un in Kulish, KALISZ, vos ikh hob bashribn fun fun di eltern oyf mir, nokh di krig.

00:19:54.994 --> 00:20:01.337
in in zeks un, draysikstn yor, zeks un fertsikstn yor.

00:20:01.595 --> 00:20:06.974
yo. un ikh hob di papirn. yo.

00:20:08.835 --> 00:20:11.794
un, vi azoy hot ir zikh gelernt?

00:20:11.794 --> 00:20:14.584
vi azoy zent ir gegangen in di lere?

00:20:16.935 --> 00:20:20.507
di tateshi iz geven a mizrakhist, a tsienist.

00:20:20.985 --> 00:20:23.311
un im's khaveyrim dos zelbe.

00:20:23.311 --> 00:20:24.861
di noente khaveyrim.

00:20:24.950 --> 00:20:30.396
hobn zey gevolt az zeyer kinder zoln geyn dem zelbn veg.

00:20:30.452 --> 00:20:31.814
hot men gebrengt

00:20:32.105 --> 00:20:36.018
tsvey lererins, eyne fun Varshe un eyne fun Lodzh,

00:20:36.018 --> 00:20:38.463
MORAH RACHEL un MORAH LUBA,

00:20:38.518 --> 00:20:41.569
vos zey hobn undz gelernt, un di kinder

00:20:41.569 --> 00:20:49.212
, kinder-gartn hot men gezungen un geredt HEBREW.

00:20:49.841 --> 00:20:51.661
m'iz aroysgeforn,

00:20:51.661 --> 00:20:54.057
m'iz geganen shpatsirn in di shtot,

00:20:54.057 --> 00:20:57.261
un in di gas hobn ale gehert az undz

00:20:57.401 --> 00:21:01.530
zingt men HEBREW, zey hobn nisht gevust sara shprakh, di, di kristn.

00:21:02.278 --> 00:21:06.359
un yedes halbe yor hot

00:21:06.359 --> 00:21:08.257
hobn zey gedungen dos teater,

00:21:08.257 --> 00:21:18.017
un me hot gemakht a a stsene un me hot geshpilt in HEBREW,

00:21:18.326 --> 00:21:20.633
ikh bin geven di primadone.

00:21:21.414 --> 00:21:23.563
ikh ken nokh biz haynt di lider!

00:21:23.068 --> 00:21:24.430
nu zing a bisl!

00:21:24.418 --> 00:21:30.549
KOL KOL KOL UNK TARNEGOL UNK LECHAY YELADIM

00:21:30.549 --> 00:21:33.525
HANECHMADIM. un azoy vayter.

00:21:33.885 --> 00:21:37.510
fun feygelekh. vi zey flien nokh Yisroel!

00:21:37.510 --> 00:21:43.448
un vi me khapt zey oyfn veg. un s'iz gevezn zeyer zeyer, far undz,

00:21:43.622 --> 00:21:46.766
ernst! m'iz gevezn, me hot es zeyer lib gehat.

00:21:46.766 --> 00:21:49.944
un me hot arayngekukt oyfn groysn bild,

00:21:49.983 --> 00:21:52.039
vos hot gehongen oyf di vant,

00:21:52.039 --> 00:21:54.551
un dos iz geven THEODOR HERZL.

00:21:55.468 --> 00:22:00.559
iz er geshtanen un arayngekukt oyf di brik un gekukt in vaser.

00:22:01.239 --> 00:22:04.930
hot men gevust az er iz der grinder fun tsionizm,

00:22:04.952 --> 00:22:08.349
un dortn vet men kumen

00:22:08.349 --> 00:22:13.063
vos vos dortn iz di himl bloy azoy vi di fon.

00:22:13.305 --> 00:22:16.709
hot men gekukt in bloyen himl, me hot gevolt flien!

00:22:19.194 --> 00:22:22.111
un dos iz geven ven ir zent geven a kleyn kind.

00:22:21.978 --> 00:22:23.213
kleyn.

00:22:23.227 --> 00:22:24.586
dernokh bin ikh, g-,

00:22:24.586 --> 00:22:25.600
dernokh,

00:22:25.600 --> 00:22:32.165
az undz ze'mir oyfgevaksn, ikh bin geganen tsvey, tsvey in a halb yor in kinder-gartn,

00:22:33.318 --> 00:22:34.393
dray yor,

00:22:34.466 --> 00:22:36.587
fun kleyn, tsvey yor alt!

00:22:36.930 --> 00:22:37.990
ikh bin gevezn,

00:22:37.990 --> 00:22:42.325
mayn bruder iz, hot ongehoybn oykh tsu geyn in dem,

00:22:42.566 --> 00:22:46.223
un dernokh iz undz shoyn nisht geven di eltern,

00:22:46.937 --> 00:22:51.741
iz shoyn nisht geven keyn FUNDUSZ, iz shoyn nisht geven keyn gelt oystsuhaltn,

00:22:53.467 --> 00:23:00.263
in a, in a kinder-gartn, in a shule. hobn zey libersht geshaft a hebreishe shule,

00:23:00.352 --> 00:23:03.621
hot men ongehoybn tsu geyn in a hebreishe shule,

00:23:03.913 --> 00:23:07.840
nor dos hot efsher ander halbn yor,

00:23:08.013 --> 00:23:10.365
tsvey yor hekhstns, ze'mir geganen,

00:23:10.365 --> 00:23:13.021
un dernokh ze'mir geganen in di PUBLIC SCHOOL.

00:23:13.852 --> 00:23:16.997
un se hot zikh ales geendert.

00:23:16.997 --> 00:23:24.074
far dem, di eltern vos zenen nisht geven oyf azoy fil int- farinteresirt un gehat

00:23:24.230 --> 00:23:30.232
FUNDUSZn, heyst es, gelt, dos iz PRIVATE, oystsuhaltn,

00:23:31.217 --> 00:23:37.945
oyf aza nivo, ze'mir gegangen shoyn in, in PUBLIC SCHOOL.

00:23:38.169 --> 00:23:41.390
un un vi azoy iz es geven tsu zayn in di PUBLIC SCHOOL?

00:23:41.325 --> 00:23:44.779
ze'mir geven tsuzamet mit kristi- kristn,

00:23:45.155 --> 00:23:47.969
ober dernokh hobn zey tseteylt.

00:23:48.868 --> 00:23:53.193
di letste tsvey yor hobn zey tseteylt.

00:23:53.193 --> 00:23:56.222
bazunder yidishe un bazunder kristn.

00:23:56.222 --> 00:23:58.130
kristn kinder.

00:23:56.974 --> 00:24:00.861
in di tsayt vos ir hot zikh gelernt tsuzamen mit di kristn,

00:24:00.900 --> 00:24:05.293
hot hot ir zikh gut adurkhgekumen mit zey? s'iz, s'iz...

00:24:05.318 --> 00:24:08.590
me hot zikh gut adurkhgekumen, nor gehaltn hot men zikh

00:24:08.595 --> 00:24:10.676
tsuzamet mit di yidishe.

00:24:10.676 --> 00:24:16.633
far dem, mit di yidishe meydlekh hob ikh kontinuirt di organizatsye.

00:24:16.633 --> 00:24:18.057
tsienistishe.

00:24:19.496 --> 00:24:21.820
hob ikh gehert tsu BEITAR,

00:24:21.960 --> 00:24:26.470
mit di zelbe kinder vos ikh hob gevaksn mit zey tsuzamet.

00:24:26.887 --> 00:24:29.295
iz gevorn gegrindet BEITAR,

00:24:30.347 --> 00:24:32.538
un me hot dortn geganen

00:24:32.538 --> 00:24:36.453
un dort getantst, un dortn geredt, un dortn gelernt,

00:24:36.453 --> 00:24:40.045
un geforn oyf KAYTANA, iz kolonye.

00:24:40.775 --> 00:24:41.428
yo.

00:24:42.885 --> 00:24:53.325
un az m'iz geforn nokh Kulish, undz, in dray un draysikstn yor,

00:24:54.107 --> 00:24:58.745
iz di organizatsye gekumen nokh Kulish,

00:24:58.745 --> 00:25:03.484
far dem, ikh hob dortn gevoynt, un dortn iz dos ershte yor geven di kolonye

00:25:03.725 --> 00:25:06.150
hinter di shtot, di kolonye, yo.

00:25:06.088 --> 00:25:07.939
ir hot gevoynt in Kulish?

00:25:08.619 --> 00:25:11.922
mayne eltern hobn zikh ibertsoygn nokh Kulish.

00:25:10.847 --> 00:25:12.309
un ven iz dos geven?

00:25:12.315 --> 00:25:14.436
in dray un draysikstn yor.

00:25:14.947 --> 00:25:16.984
un vifl zent ir demolts geven alt?

00:25:17.276 --> 00:25:18.402
densmolt

00:25:18.761 --> 00:25:22.840
bin ikh ge- alt gevezn efsher draytsn od- tsvelef yor.

00:25:23.705 --> 00:25:24.824
tsvelef yor.

00:25:24.824 --> 00:25:29.710
far dem, ikh hob frier geforn,

00:25:29.710 --> 00:25:32.106
far dem dem vi me hot zikh ibertsoygn,

00:25:32.106 --> 00:25:35.057
hob ikh geforn nokh Kulish lernen,

00:25:35.805 --> 00:25:41.081
bashprungen a yor, un gegangen in gimnazyum nokh eyn nor.

00:25:41.812 --> 00:25:44.794
far dem ikh hob mikh gelernt lataynish,

00:25:45.170 --> 00:25:46.127
ŁACINA,

00:25:46.335 --> 00:25:47.613
lataynish.

00:25:47.988 --> 00:25:52.229
un dos hob ikh gemuzt zayn forgebreyt, ikh bin gevezn, ikh hob geSTAVET,

00:25:52.229 --> 00:25:54.271
un ikh bin gegangen ⟨DO NAME-OF-SCHOOL⟩,

00:25:54.271 --> 00:25:59.391
dos iz gevezn a sh- shule vos nayntsik protsent iz gevezn,

00:25:59.565 --> 00:26:01.973
ober mer, ⟨blank⟩ kristn,

00:26:03.024 --> 00:26:06.478
nor un- undz hot men gut geredt

00:26:06.635 --> 00:26:09.127
nokh in in WIELUŃ, poylish,

00:26:10.601 --> 00:26:14.342
di tsveyte shprakh, di- hebreish,

00:26:14.516 --> 00:26:16.952
hot men nisht kontinuirt azoy,

00:26:16.952 --> 00:26:19.236
nor poylish hot men gelernt.

00:26:20.186 --> 00:26:22.020
un in der heym hot men geredt?

00:26:22.498 --> 00:26:27.724
itst, di kinder hobn geredt poylish. di eltern hobn geredt tsu undz yidish.

00:26:28.640 --> 00:26:34.535
un az ir zent oyfgevaksn in der heym, vos hot ir geredt mit ayer muter? yidish? poylish?

00:26:34.535 --> 00:26:36.533
vosere shprakh hot ir geredt in di shtub?

00:26:36.926 --> 00:26:38.693
in di shtub yidish.

00:26:38.883 --> 00:26:41.595
mit mayne kolezhankes, poylish.

00:26:43.322 --> 00:26:44.060
yo.

00:26:44.992 --> 00:26:46.556
mayn shvester

00:26:47.017 --> 00:26:50.556
iz gegan, hot geendikt in WIELUŃ, gimnazyum,

00:26:50.730 --> 00:26:53.796
iz zi geven di beste POLONISTKA!

00:26:55.303 --> 00:26:56.834
zi iz geven a yidishe.

00:26:57.159 --> 00:26:57.933
un di

00:26:57.933 --> 00:27:02.217
di do vos se, zi hot gelernt poylish iz gevezn an antisemitke.

00:27:02.812 --> 00:27:08.696
ober zi hot gezogt az mayn shvester redt ambestn poylish!

00:27:10.895 --> 00:27:14.434
un dos vos me hot gekent gut poylish,

00:27:14.777 --> 00:27:17.860
to ikh mit mayn tsvey brider,

00:27:17.915 --> 00:27:24.099
di oyskuk iz oykh geven gut, bloye oygn, hele hor, ikh hob gefarbt,

00:27:24.099 --> 00:27:26.165
me hot geredt oykh gut poylish,

00:27:26.165 --> 00:27:30.822
eyn grayz az me makht bay di daytshn,

00:27:30.822 --> 00:27:33.910
di okupatsye, eyn grayz, in poylishn,

00:27:33.910 --> 00:27:37.435
me zogt es azoy vi, a bisl vi oyf yidish,

00:27:38.317 --> 00:27:40.725
ze'mir shoyn nishto!

00:27:41.237 --> 00:27:42.498
derkenen zey!

00:27:43.110 --> 00:27:45.258
dos hot nisht getort pasirn,

00:27:45.258 --> 00:27:49.585
un bay undz iz geven di ACCENT oykhet azoy gut,

00:27:50.754 --> 00:27:54.107
ikh bin gevezn in di okupatsye oyf a

00:27:54.230 --> 00:27:55.676
f- sakh pletser

00:27:55.918 --> 00:27:58.934
ober gezogt hob ikh bin gekumen fun Poyzn,

00:27:59.057 --> 00:28:05.565
"yo, shtimt, di aktsent iz perfekt!" zey hobn dos nisht gezogt nor ge- gedenkt azoy.

00:28:06.347 --> 00:28:07.086
yo.

00:28:07.086 --> 00:28:11.550
iz yetst ober, ven ir zent oyfgevaksn in WIELUŃ,

00:28:13.451 --> 00:28:14.900
hot ir zikh gelernt

00:28:14.900 --> 00:28:18.595
tsuzamen mit di andere kristlekhe kinder, ir hot gefilt

00:28:18.595 --> 00:28:20.685
antisemitizm, in di tsayt?

00:28:21.973 --> 00:28:23.723
in WIELUŃ veynik.

00:28:27.508 --> 00:28:28.330
nor...

00:28:28.352 --> 00:28:30.440
ober in Kulish?

00:28:28.368 --> 00:28:30.607
az, in Kulish yo.

00:28:30.579 --> 00:28:35.830
 iz yetst geyt men oyfhern a minut, un me vet oyfn tsveytn TAPE CONTINUEn.
